{"tid":2274400,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"德國：呼籲美國人民保冷靜 世界需要美軍平衡邪惡勢力","createTime":"2020-11-06T11:54:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-07T04:16:28.000Z","uid":21470,"like":182,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":83,"replies":[{"pid":"48f2e2ece95231cf148a90d684ae56eea440629d","tid":2274400,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T11:54:05.000Z","msg":"德國外長籲美民主共和兩營陣保持冷靜直至大選有結果<br />\n<br />\n德國外長馬斯評論美國大選，指美國不是一場獨角戲，任何人繼續火上加油都是不負責任，呼籲民主共和兩黨陣營保持冷靜，直至出現獲獨立確認的大選結果。他又認為，一個體面的失敗者，比起一個耀眼的勝利者，對民主制度的運作更為重要。<br />\n<br />\n馬斯又預期，當大選有結果後，美國可能暫時不能全面回到國際舞台，但指世界需要美國作為維持秩序的力量，而並非混亂的因素。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2365161\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2365161&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9oICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=8fa563f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2365161</a>"},{"pid":"2a8b132a82dd34e53b83ef84a779bc51d6634274","tid":2274400,"uid":79793,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T11:55:54.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">治國、平天下</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"748aa6af8e6ea54de2ccb41184027acbb9640173","tid":2274400,"uid":68620,"like":131,"dislike":1,"score":130,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T11:56:37.000Z","msg":"邪惡=中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1d89ac5c9d5970c321cd81c82606c4915eff02d","tid":2274400,"uid":189015,"like":182,"dislike":2,"score":180,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T11:59:08.000Z","msg":"拜登當選嘅話呢4年都唔駛見到美國出嚟維持秩序<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8552397d1479af51edff98e851e41719d595a00e","tid":2274400,"uid":51932,"like":128,"dislike":1,"score":127,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T11:59:13.000Z","msg":"咁你德國佬又唔肯俾錢, 垃圾<i